data.description: Wonderful, resort style living in Harlan Ranch, of Clovis CA. Featuring Five bedrooms, master and two additional bedrooms downstairs, plus Two additional bedrooms and a Loft upstairs. Beautiful durable flooring. Formal dining, living, and family room. Gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar, pantry, granite counters, stainless appliances. Overhead ceiling fans and lighting. Enjoy the private Outdoor space, with pergola, gazebo, raised patios, spa, fruit trees (pomegranate, grapefruit, plum & more) Find energy efficient features such as solar, tank-less water heater, 4zone HVAC system. Long lasting Tile Roof. 3 car tandem garage. One of the prime locations within Harlan Ranch, with sidewalks, and larger yards. Notice the community with park like settings, and barbecue areas nearby, Community pool, and fun social events await you.
